
## ğŸš€ Features

- **Responsive Design**: Fully responsive layout compatible with all screen sizes.
- **Smooth Scrolling**: JavaScript-powered smooth transitions between sections.
- **Typing Effect**: A typewriter animation displays the user's name on the hero section.
- **Parallax Effect**: Scroll-based visual motion for the hero section.
- **Interactive Navbar**:
  - Dynamic background on scroll.
  - Auto-highlighted active section links.
- **Fade-in Animations**: Section content appears with smooth animation on scroll using Intersection Observer.
- **Mobile Menu Toggle**: Hamburger menu functionality for mobile devices.
- **Contact Section**: Displays contact info and social links with icons.
- **Education & Certifications**:
  - Timeline layout presenting education and professional certifications using appropriate icons.

